WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
I was just looking at the St Patrick's Church here in San Francisco.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.000
I want to know how tall it is.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
I think we have the skills to answer that question.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Some relevant facts.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:17.000
Right now, my head is about 1 m above the height of the camera lens,

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:19.000
and the camera is about 2 meters in front of me.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:23.000
The church is about 90 meters behind me,

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:28.000
and notice that the top of the church lines up perfectly with the top of my head.

00:00:28.000 --> 99:59:59.000
I want you to tell me how tall is the St Patrick's Church and give your answer in meters.

